# tshy dual-build temp artifacts (packages/remote-control-contract).
# `.tshy/` holds tshy's generated scratch tsconfigs; `.tshy-build/` is its
# scratch outDir; `src/package.json` is the per-dialect type marker tshy
# drops during the CJS pass.
